summary.span: 类表示 Exchange 存储中的泛型项目。

span.span: The class represents a generic item in the Exchange store.

span.para: 对象表示电子邮件和非 Exchange Web Services (EWS) 架构的强类型的所有其他项目。如 IPM 的项目。共享和以返回 IPM.InfoPath对象。启动与 Exchange Server 2010 和 Exchange Online 的 Exchange 版本不返回基在响应中的对象。
The class is the base type for the , , , and classes.

objects represent e-mail messages and all other items that are not strongly typed by the Exchange Web Services (EWS) schema. Items such as IPM.Sharing and IPM.InfoPath are returned as objects. Versions of Exchange starting with Exchange Server 2010 and Exchange Online do not return the base object in responses.
